CaptainK9's 'Veggie Mix' is made from our very own special blend of fresh green ingredients.  Providing a healthy addition to the raw meat diet.  A highly recommend addition to your regular meat addition.

Ingredients: Kelp, cucumber, carrot, broccoli, kale, celery, pumpkin, Spinach, green bean, organic apple, blueberry, strawberry, cantaloupe, kiwi, coconut oil and probiotics supplements.

Price per LB - $6.99
